Transifex.com
=============

The website transifex.com.

Dependancies
------------

* On Fedora run: 
  * ``yum install Django python-markdown python-openid python-httplib2``

* [http://code.google.com/p/django-tagging django-tagging]
* [http://code.google.com/p/django_authopenid django_authopenid]
* [http://code.google.com/p/django-pagination django-pagination]
* [http://code.google.com/p/django-contact-form django-contact_form]
* For notifications:
 - [http://code.google.com/p/django-notification django-notification]
 - [http://code.google.com/p/django-atompub/ django-atompub]
* Markdown

Install
-------

* Customize ``settings.py`` and ``urls.py``.
* Run ``./manage.py syncdb``
* Run ``./manage.py runserver 8088``.

To enable debugging, run the server as follows:

``./manage.py runserver --settings settings_debug``  

Testing
-------

``./manage.py test``